summary:
I am an experienced graduate with a demonstrated history of working in the political organization industry.
Through my academic and professional experience, I have gained valuable skills in Political Strategy and Political Communication, Team Building, Public Speaking, and International Relations. 

All in all, I would describe myself as a strong professional with a Bachelor of Science - BS focused in Political Science and Government from the University of Cyprus and a Masters of Arts - MA focused in European Studies with a specialization in International Relations from the University of Maastricht.
